title: Being Creative - Emilee and Chad
description:
Emilee (Mudhut) and Chad talk about the creative process, the hidden springs of Meaning while creating art, and being created by art during creation.
They explore being audience ( dialogue with the medium i.e., film, music, paintings, poetry), the world of a child’s imagination, and they share their desires and hopes for what might come next in this corner of the Internet.
